{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji28.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给文运昌的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给文运昌的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1950年4月19日）运昌仁兄如唔："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接到了你的许多信，感谢你的好意，因忙迟复为歉。吾兄健存，儿孙众多，可为庆贺。地方工作缺点甚多，应当纠正。如有所见，尚望随时见告。泽民泽覃\"均已殉难，知注并闻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺颂安吉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五○年四月十九日[1]泽民，即毛泽民。泽覃，即毛泽覃。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":4,"day":19}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":303,"page_end":303},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}